descriptionNullable:
# NFT Historical sales data
The dataset consists of opensea NFT sales transactions recorded between 1 February 2021 and 28 February 2021.
code used to create the dataset: https://github.com/Checco9811/opensea-api-nft-sales.

## Content
The dataset consist of a .csv file with the following attributes:
- **collections_slug**: unique identifier of the collection
- **collection_name**: name of the collection
- **collection_url**: url of the collection
- **asset_id**: identifier of the asset sold
- **asset_name**: name of the asset sold
- **asset_description**: description of the asset sold
- **asset_contract_date**: the asset contract address creation date
- **asset_url**: url of the asset sold
- **asset_image_url**: image url of the asset sold
- **event_id**: unique identifier of the transaction
- **event_time**: when the event was recorded
- **event_auction_type**: auction type
- **event_contract_address**: the event contract address
- **event_quantity**: The amount of the item that was sold
- **event_payment_symbol**: the payment asset used in this transaction, such as ETH, WETH or DAI
- **event_total_price**: The total price that the asset was bought for

CREDIT: https://opensea.io/
